title: Ep. 804 - WIll Jetha Return? - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The army asks Sodhi and the others to return but thye refuse to do os. On the other hand, Daya refuses to eat her food thinking of Jetha who wouldn't have eaten as well.

title: Ep. 805 - Finding Help - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sodhi and the others decide to go to Delhi to  make sure that matter resolves soon. They take help from a localite for the same. The residents also pray for a solution soon.

title: Ep. 806 - Daya Asks For Help - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sodhi's friends have come to visit him and help them. Sundar receives a text asking for help. He recommends a minsiter's name. Daya runs around in need of help from various ministers while Jetha's situation deteriorates.

title: Ep. 807 - Attempts Fail - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: As there is no help from the minister, Daya goes to the embassy in need of a visa to Pakistan. That attempt fails too. Jetha and Daya finally talk over a phone call. He is called over by the head for further investigation.

title: Ep. 808 - Good News - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya decides to make her last attempt in rescuing Jetha. They go to a temple wishing for the good.  The Pakistan army has still not given up questioning him. Meanwhile, a good news knocks the door of Champaklal.

title: Ep. 809 - Jetha Finally Returns - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: After all the bad news and hurdles, Jetha is finally out from the jail. Everybody is celebrating the happy moment. Daya and Jetha are elated to see each other.

title: Ep. 810 - A Feast - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: There's happiness all over with Jetha's arrival. A feast is organised in view of the same. The people of Gokuldham celebrate the happiness. Jetha makes a promise to Daya.

title: Ep. 811 - Sundar's Love For Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Sundar is excited to come back and meet Jethalal as he's returned from Pakistan and wants to spend some quality time with him.

title: Ep. 812 - A Lonesome Popatlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal is disappointed over the fact that the gods above aren't listening to his prayers and requests them to make his one and only wish come true, that is to find a life partner!

title: Ep. 813 - Dr. Haathi Has A Proposal For Popatlal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Dr. Haathi is testing his regular patient that happens to be his chaacha ji, and asks him that why is it he's maintaining a poor lifestyle to which he replies by saying he's tensed for his daughter's marriage as they want to find a good groom.

title: Ep. 814 - Daya Has A Plan - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: The Haathi family, along with Popatlal are worried as to how will he manage to see both the girls at the same time. To which, Daya has a fantastic plan! Watch to find out what her plan is!

title: Ep. 815 - Popatlal Is Determined To Win Hearts - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal is finally ready to meet the girls and has realized that it's a tough task that he has to go back and forth, but is determined that he will do, and puts up a great task!

title: Ep. 816 - Popatlal's Greed - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal is constantly going back and forth from Daya's place to Dr. Haathi's place as he wants to impress both the girls and wants to give both a try. Will he succeed?

title: Ep. 817 - Popatlal's Life Decision - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Dr. Haathi and Bhide are getting restless that Popatlal is missing as he has to make a decision between the 2 girls, and in the hurry he ends up himself in a big trouble! What could it be?

title: Ep. 818 - Popatlal's Birthday Party - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Popatlal gets kidnapped from his sleep and is escorted to the club house where later he realizes that the whole society members had planned this to surprise him his birthday party! Popatlal is touched by everyone!
